result.title: Indeed Prime is looking for talent!
result.content:
Check out Indeed Prime.

Full disclosure: referral link. But I got my job through Indeed Prime, so I really do recommend it.

Top 5% of candidates pass the coding assessment. Selective, but you don't have to be a red coder. Imagine if hundreds of companies sponsor a contest -- and you win. That's the level of interest you'll get.

EDIT: Downvotes?
